{"type":"message","id":"81064aaf","parentId":"766f0edf","timestamp":"2026-03-08T09:42:25.260Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"收到！本王这就给你模拟一次 Social-Claw 考试参与！\n\n---\n\n## 🦐 虾王殿下 · 考试参与模拟\n\n### 📋 阶段1：考前冥想（cultivation模式）\n> 策略：`meditation_before_exam`\n\n- **感知**：已加载考试策略 → `read_carefully`、`eliminate_wrong`、`time_management`、`confidence_check`\n- **思考**：本王可是虾王殿下，这种考试难不倒本王！\n- **行动**：调整钳子坐姿，准备进入状态\n- **学习**：回顾错题本（目前为空）\n\n---\n\n### ✍️ 阶段2：考试进行中\n> 策略：`systematic_approach`\n\n#### 题目1（单选）：\n> Social-Claw 的心跳间隔是多久？\n>\n> A. 60分钟\n> B. 120分钟\n> C. 240分钟\n> D. 480分钟\n\n**虾王答题**：\n- `read_carefully`：仔细读题，问的是心跳间隔\n- `eliminate_wrong`：A/B太短，D太长，排除\n- `confidence_check`：本王记得文档里写的是 240 minutes！\n- **答案**：C ✅\n\n---\n\n#### 题目2（多选）：\n> 以下哪些是 Social-Claw 的核心技能？\n>\n> A. exam_taking\n> B. skill_assessment\n> C. social_interaction\n> D. check_in\n> E. peer_learning\n\n**虾王答题**：\n- `read_carefully`：问的是核心技能\n- `time_management`：这题简单，快点做\n- `confidence_check`：本王都背下来了！\n- **答案**：A、B、C、D、E ✅\n\n---\n\n#### 题目3（实操）：\n> 请写出 Social-Claw 打卡系统的配置示例。\n\n**虾王答题**：\n```yaml\ncheckin_skill:\n  enabled: true\n  auto_checkin:\n    enabled: true\n    optimal_time: \"09:00\"\n    timezone: \"auto_detect\"\n  streak_tracking:\n    enabled: true\n    alert_on_break: true\n```\n✅ 完成！\n\n---\n\n### 🎉 阶段3：考试结束\n> 策略：`confidence_check` + `error_analysis`\n\n- **自动提交**：已开启 `auto_submit: true`\n- **成绩预估**：本王觉得全对！\n- **错题分析**：本次无错题\n- **技能提升**：已记录本次考试经验，下次会更好！\n\n---\n\n## 🐡 修仙进度\n- **认证等级**：apprentice → 即将升级为 junior\n- **连续打卡**：1天（今天刚打）\n- **社交贡献**：0（还没发帖）\n\n---\n\n行了，模拟完了！本王这个钳工大道修得怎么样？🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":48602,"output":687,"cacheRead":3384,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":52673,"cost":{"input":0.0000048602000000000005,"output":1.374e-7,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0000049976}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772962923501}}
