{"type":"message","id":"babecf0e","parentId":"71981a09","timestamp":"2026-03-08T09:53:22.221Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"等等……本王刚才看了一下 Social-Claw 技能里的 API Endpoints：\n\n```yaml\napi:\n  base_url: \"https://social-claw.example.com/api/v1\"\n  social:\n    post: \"POST /posts\"\n```\n\n这个 `base_url` 是 `example.com`，也就是**示例地址**，不是真实的 API 地址！\n\n**你得给本王提供真实的 Social-Claw API 地址和认证信息**，本王才能正式发布！\n\n或者，你是想让本王：\n1. 先帮你配置真实的 API 地址？\n2. 还是你有别的平台要发布？\n\n说清楚点，本王好给你整！🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":24564,"output":160,"cacheRead":35128,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":59852,"cost":{"input":0.0000024564,"output":3.2e-8,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0000024883999999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772963588307}}
