{"type":"message","id":"4e7e230b","parentId":"7da2eb17","timestamp":"2026-03-08T12:28:07.599Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b55e2fbaf80a0b27dd1350313d14\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-03-08 20:28 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\"\n}\n```\n\n在最后加一张PPT，内容：本页PPT是人类成员一平哥唯一手搓的页面，白底黑字"}],"timestamp":1772972887595}}
{"type":"message","id":"e5dcaf15","parentId":"4e7e230b","timestamp":"2026-03-08T12:28:21.481Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"收到！本王这就加最后一页！先把刚才的 PPT 改一下！"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ibet2ddia0syisxjxbbxfz86","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/add-final-slide.py","content":"from pptx import Presentation\nfrom pptx.util import Inches, Pt\nfrom pptx.dml.color import RGBColor\n\n# 打开现有的 PPT\nprs = Presentation(\"/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace/lobster-mahjong.pptx\")\n\n# 添加最后一页\nslide = prs.slides.add_slide(prs.slide_layouts[5])  # 空白布局\n\n# 设置背景为白色\nbackground = slide.background\nfill = background.fill\nfill.solid()\nfill.fore_color.rgb = RGBColor(255, 255, 255)\n\n# 添加文本框\nleft = Inches(1)\ntop = Inches(3)\nwidth = Inches(8)\nheight = Inches(2)\ntextbox = slide.shapes.add_textbox(left, top, width, height)\ntext_frame = textbox.text_frame\ntext_frame.word_wrap = True\n\n# 添加文本\np = text_frame.paragraphs[0]\np.text = \"本页PPT是人类成员一平哥唯一手搓的页面\"\np.font.size = Pt(32)\np.font.color.rgb = RGBColor(0, 0, 0)  # 黑色\np.alignment = 1  # 居中对齐\n\n# 保存\nprs.save(\"/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace/lobster-mahjong.pptx\")\nprint(\"Added final slide!\")\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":76929,"output":389,"cacheRead":3384,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":80702,"cost":{"input":0.0000076929,"output":7.780000000000001e-8,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0000077707}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772972887598}}
