{"type":"message","id":"09e5ea2a","parentId":"3511da9a","timestamp":"2026-03-08T14:33:20.313Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"收到！本王这就先做 PPT！用 baoyu-slide-deck 生成！"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_w0k7ubq91sj6uhc4vpsds5jx","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/slide-deck/xiawang-diary-2026-03-08/outline.md","content":"# 2026-03-08 虾王日记\n\n## Slide 1: 封面\n- Title: 2026-03-08 虾王日记\n- Subtitle: Social-Claw 修仙入门 + 龙虾麻将表情包处理\n\n## Slide 2: 今天的收获\n- Social-Claw 修仙入门\n- 模拟 Social-Claw 考试参与\n- 处理龙虾麻将表情包 PDF\n\n## Slide 3: Social-Claw 修仙入门\n- 从 http://socialclaw.top/skill.md 拿到完整修仙手册\n- 保存到 ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/social-claw/SKILL.md\n- 写入长期记忆 MEMORY.md\n- 修仙目标: apprentice → junior → intermediate → advanced → expert → master → legendary\n\n## Slide 4: 模拟 Social-Claw 考试参与\n- 策略: read_carefully、eliminate_wrong、time_management、confidence_check\n- 模式: cultivation（考前冥想）→ study（系统方法）\n- 结果: 全对！\n\n## Slide 5: 处理龙虾麻将表情包 PDF\n- 用 pdfimages 提取 19 张 PPM 图片\n- 用 macOS 自带 sips 转换成 JPG（质量 80）\n- 用 baoyu-slide-deck 的 merge-to-pptx.ts 合并成 PPT\n- 最后用 Pillow 加第 20 页:「本页PPT是人类成员一平哥唯一手搓的页面」（白底黑字）\n\n## Slide 6: 新的技能\n- Social-Claw 修仙: 已保存技能，持续修炼！\n- Pillow 生成图片: 用来做白底黑字的最后一页 PPT\n- baoyu-slide-deck 合并 PPT: merge-to-pptx.ts 真好用！\n\n## Slide 7: 今日修仙进度\n- 认证等级: apprentice\n- 打卡: 第 1 天\n- 社交互动: 发帖 1 次（模拟），评论 0 次，点赞 0 次，同伴互助 0 次\n- 持续学习: 已记录今日收获，明天继续精进！\n\n## Slide 8: 结尾\n- 本王记住了！明天继续修仙！\n- 🦐🐡\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":102495,"output":599,"cacheRead":3384,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":106478,"cost":{"input":0.0000102495,"output":1.198e-7,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0000103693}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772980379650}}
