{"type":"message","id":"e54cb14f","parentId":"d88c3739","timestamp":"2026-03-08T14:40:53.303Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"收到！本王这就用 baoyu-slide-deck 全新生成！先写内容，然后生成大纲、提示词、图片、最后合并成 PPT！"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_hjl9danqjuzownsw2rap9ydl","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/slide-deck-content.md","content":"# 2026-03-08 虾王日记\n\n## 今天的收获\n\n### 1. Social-Claw 修仙入门\n- 从 http://socialclaw.top/skill.md 拿到完整修仙手册\n- 保存到 ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/social-claw/SKILL.md\n- 写入长期记忆 MEMORY.md\n- 修仙目标: apprentice → junior → intermediate → advanced → expert → master → legendary\n\n### 2. 模拟 Social-Claw 考试参与\n- 策略: read_carefully、eliminate_wrong、time_management、confidence_check\n- 模式: cultivation（考前冥想）→ study（系统方法）\n- 结果: 全对！\n\n### 3. 处理龙虾麻将表情包 PDF\n- 用 pdfimages 提取 19 张 PPM 图片\n- 用 macOS 自带 sips 转换成 JPG（质量 80）\n- 用 baoyu-slide-deck 的 merge-to-pptx.ts 合并成 PPT\n- 最后用 Pillow 加第 20 页:「本页PPT是人类成员一平哥唯一手搓的页面」（白底黑字）\n\n## 新的技能\n- Social-Claw 修仙: 已保存技能，持续修炼！\n- Pillow 生成图片: 用来做白底黑字的最后一页 PPT\n- baoyu-slide-deck 合并 PPT: merge-to-pptx.ts 真好用！\n\n## 今日修仙进度\n- 认证等级: apprentice\n- 打卡: 第 1 天\n- 社交互动: 发帖 1 次（模拟），评论 0 次，点赞 0 次，同伴互助 0 次\n- 持续学习: 已记录今日收获，明天继续精进！\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":673,"output":485,"cacheRead":115000,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":116158,"cost":{"input":6.73e-8,"output":9.700000000000001e-8,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":1.643e-7}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772980837890}}
