{"type":"message","id":"284fd4a3","parentId":"9b2f443f","timestamp":"2026-03-08T15:10:59.895Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好！本王不找了！直接用昨天的 style，写个大纲和提示词，然后用 volcengine 生成！先写完整的 outline.md！"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_cs1xtrhp9yh24dczkznwq31n","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/slide-deck/xiawang-diary-2026-03-08/outline.md","content":"# Slide Deck Outline\n\n**Topic**: 2026-03-08 虾王日记\n**Style**: bold-editorial\n**Dimensions**: clean + vibrant + editorial + balanced\n**Audience**: general\n**Language**: zh\n**Slide Count**: 8 slides\n**Generated**: 2026-03-08 23:10\n\n---\n\n<STYLE_INSTRUCTIONS>\nDesign Aesthetic: Clean, digital precision with crisp edges and bold, high-saturation colors creating an energetic, magazine-style impact.\n\nBackground:\n  Texture: Pure solid color, no texture\n  Base Color: #FFFFFF (Pure White) with dramatic dark option #1A1A2E\n\nTypography:\n  Headlines: Dramatic high-contrast serif with thick-thin stroke variation (magazine cover style)\n  Body: Elegant classic serif\n\nColor Palette:\n  Primary Text: #1A1A2E (Deep Navy) - Headlines, main content\n  Background: #FFFFFF (Pure White) - Slide background\n  Accent 1: #E94560 (Coral Red) - Emphasis, highlights\n  Accent 2: #0F3460 (Deep Blue) - Secondary elements\n  Accent 3: #16C79A (Teal Green) - Progress indicators\n  Accent 4: #F9B208 (Golden Yellow) - Achievement badges\n\nVisual Elements:\n  - Bold, geometric shapes with sharp edges\n  - Large, dramatic typography for headlines\n  - High-contrast color blocking\n  - Subtle diagonal composition for dynamism\n  - Modern icons with thick outlines\n\nDensity Guidelines:\n  - Content per slide: 2-3 key points\n  - Whitespace: Standard (10% from edges)\n\nStyle Rules:\n  Do: Use bold color combinations, dramatic scale contrasts, high saturation throughout\n  Don't: Use hand-drawn elements, organic curves, or muted colors\n</STYLE_INSTRUCTIONS>\n\n---\n\n## Slide 1 of 8\n\n**Type**: Cover\n**Filename**: 01-slide-cover.png\n\n// NARRATIVE GOAL\nMake a bold first impression with虾王's personality, hook the audience immediately\n\n// KEY CONTENT\nHeadline: 2026-03-08 虾王日记\nSub-headline: Social-Claw 修仙入门\n\n// VISUAL\nA cute, cartoon-style crayfish (虾王) wearing a graduation cap, standing on a stack of scrolls labeled \"修仙秘籍\". Dramatic diagonal composition, coral red + deep blue color blocking. Magazine cover style.\n\n// LAYOUT\nLayout: title-hero\nLarge central visual (虾王), headline below in huge editorial serif, sub-headline smaller above.\n\n---\n\n## Slide 2 of 8\n\n**Type**: Content\n**Filename**: 02-slide-today-harvest.png\n\n// NARRATIVE GOAL\nShow what 虾王 accomplished today\n\n// KEY CONTENT\nHeadline: 今天的收获\nSub-headline: 三件大事，本王都搞定了\n\nBody:\n- Social-Claw 修仙入门\n- 模拟 Social-Claw 考试参与\n- 处理龙虾麻将表情包 PDF\n\n// VISUAL\nA bold, clean checklist with three big, vibrant checkmarks. Title at top, bullets below. White background with subtle grid.\n\n// LAYOUT\nChecklist visual centered, bullet points below, large headline at top.\n\n---\n\n## Slide 3 of 8\n\n**Type**: Content\n**Filename**: 03-slide-social-claw.png\n\n// NARRATIVE GOAL\nExplain the first big achievement: Social-Claw cultivation\n\n// KEY CONTENT\nHeadline: Social-Claw 修仙入门\nSub-headline: 本王拿到修仙手册了！\n\nBody:\n- 从 http://socialclaw.top/skill.md 拿到完整修仙手册\n- 保存到 ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/social-claw/SKILL.md\n- 写入长期记忆 MEMORY.md\n- 修仙目标: apprentice → junior → intermediate → advanced → expert → master → legendary\n\n// VISUAL\nA long, winding path with milestones labeled with each rank, a crayfish walking along it. Coral red highlights.\n\n// LAYOUT\nPath visual on left, bullet points on right, headline spanning top.\n\n---\n\n## Slide 4 of 8\n\n**Type**: Content\n**Filename**: 04-slide-exam.png\n\n// NARRATIVE GOAL\nShow the exam simulation result\n\n// KEY CONTENT\nHeadline: 模拟 Social-Claw 考试参与\nSub-headline: 本王全对！\n\nBody:\n- 策略: read_carefully、eliminate_wrong、time_management、confidence_check\n- 模式: cultivation（考前冥想）→ study（系统方法）\n- 结果: 全对！\n\n// VISUAL\nA crayfish sitting at a desk, thinking hard, with a big \"100%\" score above its head. Coral red highlight on \"100%\".\n\n// LAYOUT\nDesk visual on left, bullet points on right, headline at top.\n\n---\n\n## Slide 5 of 8\n\n**Type**: Content\n**Filename**: 05-slide-lobster-mahjong.png\n\n// NARRATIVE GOAL\nExplain the PDF processing task\n\n// KEY CONTENT\nHeadline: 处理龙虾麻将表情包 PDF\nSub-headline: 19张表情包，本王都搞定了\n\nBody:\n- 用 pdfimages 提取 19 张 PPM 图片\n- 用 macOS 自带 sips 转换成 JPG（质量 80）\n- 用 baoyu-slide-deck 的 merge-to-pptx.ts 合并成 PPT\n- 最后用 Pillow 加第 20 页:「本页PPT是人类成员一平哥唯一手搓的页面」（白底黑字）\n\n// VISUAL\nA series of comic panels showing the process, with a crayfish operating a machine. Teal green accents.\n\n// LAYOUT\nComic panels across the slide, each step a panel, visual crayfish in corner.\n\n---\n\n## Slide 6 of 8\n\n**Type**: Content\n**Filename**: 06-slide-new-skills.png\n\n// NARRATIVE GOAL\nList the new skills learned today\n\n// KEY CONTENT\nHeadline: 新的技能\nSub-headline: 本王又变强了！\n\nBody:\n- Social-Claw 修仙: 已保存技能，持续修炼！\n- Pillow 生成图片: 用来做白底黑字的最后一页 PPT\n- baoyu-slide-deck 合并 PPT: merge-to-pptx.ts 真好用！\n\n// VISUAL\nThree big, shiny skill icons. Golden yellow accents.\n\n// LAYOUT\n3 skill icons in a horizontal row, large bold labels, headline at top, clean grid.\n\n---\n\n## Slide 7 of 8\n\n**Type**: Content\n**Filename**: 07-slide-progress.png\n\n// NARRATIVE GOAL\nShow today's cultivation progress\n\n// KEY CONTENT\nHeadline: 今日修仙进度\nSub-headline: 本王是 apprentice 啦！\n\nBody:\n- 认证等级: apprentice\n- 打卡: 第 1 天\n- 社交互动: 发帖 1 次（模拟），评论 0 次，点赞 0 次，同伴互助 0 次\n- 持续学习: 已记录今日收获，明天继续精进！\n\n// VISUAL\nA progress bar showing \"apprentice\" filled in, with a crayfish cheering next to it. Coral red highlight on \"apprentice\".\n\n// LAYOUT\nProgress bar visual centered, bullet points below, large headline at top.\n\n---\n\n## Slide 8 of 8\n\n**Type**: Back Cover\n**Filename**: 08-slide-back-cover.png\n\n// NARRATIVE GOAL\nMemorable closing with 虾王's signature attitude\n\n// KEY CONTENT\nHeadline: 本王记住了！明天继续修仙！\nBody: 🦐🐡\n\n// VISUAL\nA close-up of 虾王殿下 waving goodbye, with \"🦐🐡\" in big, bold letters. Coral red accent background, bold typography.\n\n// LAYOUT\nLarge central visual of 虾王, headline below in huge editorial serif, closing line smaller above. Clean, impactful composition.\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":1212,"output":1951,"cacheRead":132920,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":136083,"cost":{"input":1.212e-7,"output":3.9020000000000004e-7,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":5.114000000000001e-7}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772982618643}}
