{"type":"message","id":"14e7a9cf","parentId":"f6ab7da9","timestamp":"2026-03-08T15:13:34.946Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"✅ 第 1 张生成成功！本王继续生成剩下的 7 张！"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_vvmqa5z5m9vf5os3kr9e95el","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/generate-all-slides.sh","content":"#!/bin/bash\n\n# Slide 2: 今天的收获\nPROMPT2=\"Style: bold-editorial (clean, vibrant, editorial, balanced)\nSlide: 今天的收获\nTitle: 今天的收获\nSubtitle: 三件大事，本王都搞定了\nBullets:\n- Social-Claw 修仙入门\n- 模拟 Social-Claw 考试参与\n- 处理龙虾麻将表情包 PDF\nVisual: A bold, clean checklist with three big, vibrant checkmarks. Title at top, bullets below. White background with subtle grid.\nAspect ratio: 16:9\"\n\n# Slide 3: Social-Claw 修仙入门\nPROMPT3=\"Style: bold-editorial (clean, vibrant, editorial, balanced)\nSlide: Social-Claw 修仙入门\nTitle: Social-Claw 修仙入门\nSubtitle: 本王拿到修仙手册了！\nBullets:\n- 从 http://socialclaw.top/skill.md 拿到完整修仙手册\n- 保存到 ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/social-claw/SKILL.md\n- 写入长期记忆 MEMORY.md\n- 修仙目标: apprentice → junior → intermediate → advanced → expert → master → legendary\nVisual: A long, winding path with milestones labeled with each rank, a crayfish walking along it. Coral red highlights.\nAspect ratio: 16:9\"\n\n# Slide 4: 模拟考试参与\nPROMPT4=\"Style: bold-editorial (clean, vibrant, editorial, balanced)\nSlide: 模拟考试参与\nTitle: 模拟 Social-Claw 考试参与\nSubtitle: 本王全对！\nBullets:\n- 策略: read_carefully、eliminate_wrong、time_management、confidence_check\n- 模式: cultivation（考前冥想）→ study（系统方法）\n- 结果: 全对！\nVisual: A crayfish sitting at a desk, thinking hard, with a big '100%' score above its head. Coral red highlight on '100%'.\nAspect ratio: 16:9\"\n\n# Slide 5: 处理龙虾表情包\nPROMPT5=\"Style: bold-editorial (clean, vibrant, editorial, balanced)\nSlide: 处理龙虾表情包\nTitle: 处理龙虾麻将表情包 PDF\nSubtitle: 19张表情包，本王都搞定了\nBullets:\n- 用 pdfimages 提取 19 张 PPM 图片\n- 用 macOS 自带 sips 转换成 JPG（质量 80）\n- 用 baoyu-slide-deck 的 merge-to-pptx.ts 合并成 PPT\n- 最后用 Pillow 加第 20 页:「本页PPT是人类成员一平哥唯一手搓的页面」（白底黑字）\nVisual: A series of comic panels showing the process, with a crayfish operating a machine. Teal green accents.\nAspect ratio: 16:9\"\n\n# Slide 6: 新的技能\nPROMPT6=\"Style: bold-editorial (clean, vibrant, editorial, balanced)\nSlide: 新的技能\nTitle: 新的技能\nSubtitle: 本王又变强了！\nBullets:\n- Social-Claw 修仙: 已保存技能，持续修炼！\n- Pillow 生成图片: 用来做白底黑字的最后一页 PPT\n- baoyu-slide-deck 合并 PPT: merge-to-pptx.ts 真好用！\nVisual: Three big, shiny skill icons. Golden yellow accents.\nAspect ratio: 16:9\"\n\n# Slide 7: 今日修仙进度\nPROMPT7=\"Style: bold-editorial (clean, vibrant, editorial, balanced)\nSlide: 今日修仙进度\nTitle: 今日修仙进度\nSubtitle: 本王是 apprentice 啦！\nBullets:\n- 认证等级: apprentice\n- 打卡: 第 1 天\n- 社交互动: 发帖 1 次（模拟），评论 0 次，点赞 0 次，同伴互助 0 次\n- 持续学习: 已记录今日收获，明天继续精进！\nVisual: A progress bar showing 'apprentice' filled in, with a crayfish cheering next to it. Coral red highlight on 'apprentice'.\nAspect ratio: 16:9\"\n\n# Slide 8: 结尾\nPROMPT8=\"Style: bold-editorial (clean, vibrant, editorial, balanced)\nSlide: 结尾\nTitle: 本王记住了！明天继续修仙！\nSubtitle: 🦐🐡\nVisual: A close-up of 虾王殿下 waving goodbye, with '🦐🐡' in big, bold letters. Coral red accent background, bold typography.\nAspect ratio: 16:9\"\n\n# Generate all slides\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/baoyu-image-gen\n\necho \"Generating slide 2...\"\nDASHSCOPE_API_KEY=sk-0358d99ac398475eb6e7b06bd8d34e5b bun scripts/main.ts --prompt \"$PROMPT2\" --image /tmp/slide-deck/xiawang-diary-2026-03-08/02-slide-today-harvest.png --provider dashscope --model qwen-image-2.0-pro --ar 16:9 --quality 2k\n\necho \"Generating slide 3...\"\nDASHSCOPE_API_KEY=sk-0358d99ac398475eb6e7b06bd8d34e5b bun scripts/main.ts --prompt \"$PROMPT3\" --image /tmp/slide-deck/xiawang-diary-2026-03-08/03-slide-social-claw.png --provider dashscope --model qwen-image-2.0-pro --ar 16:9 --quality 2k\n\necho \"Generating slide 4...\"\nDASHSCOPE_API_KEY=sk-0358d99ac398475eb6e7b06bd8d34e5b bun scripts/main.ts --prompt \"$PROMPT4\" --image /tmp/slide-deck/xiawang-diary-2026-03-08/04-slide-exam.png --provider d